				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Very good ideas... I especially like the extended research time...
<br />

<br />
An extended time to research all the techs would make the start of the game longer, which I think is healthy for all players.
<br />

<br />
It would make it harder for a n00b to jump right into the game and become super powerful within a mere week or two.
<br />

<br />
If there's a longer period for techs, then the research stat would be more valuable early on, and would encourage people to build and keep research labs... As well as choose races not so often used, that have good research bonuses.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-style: italic">Gamer through and through</span>
