				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Isntead of extended research, which I think is a great idea, I beleive it would be better to just increase the tech tree with a whloe lot of projects and techs that have smaller impacts, like.
<br />

<br />
Compact crystal -10% space used for lvl 1 and 2 weapons, can be up to lvl 2.
<br />

<br />
Lots of projects that do like.
<br />

<br />
-5% ships build time.
<br />
lng range radars to decrease expedition time etc...
<br />

<br />
This way, if I am playing for say, 3 months straight, there will always be something other than fleeting to do. Also, I think it would be great to have some way to build defensive structures on planets for a high cost etc.
<br />

<br />
Devices. There shold be more devices, and the ability to add say, 2 boosters to a battlevruiser or something...to make it a more effective flanking vessal.
<br />

<br />
ITs really bother some when I goto work, and during that time I get appointed rank and it expires before I get off work.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
