				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Would you guys PLEASE notice this was posted over a year ago and has been ignored that long. Your project idea is absolutely braindead, there are many projects that without being in conjunction with another they are more of a hinderence than a help. Projects customize your empire, you don't like mili cm being so high? Buy your projects accordingly and independent and get the council projects accordingly. Your military CM idea is a mega nerf for the races that are *meant* to be in industry mode with top military CM, that;s how they are.
<br />

<br />
the allied fleet idea has been discussed, but your ranges make it so you invalidate allied fleets to a large extent, at the power levels you are suggesting it doesn't add much help. These allied fleets are a million times more balanced than they used to be and they are almost perfect as they are now.
<br />

<br />
Renaming fleets-&gt;Understandable, not implemented yet for unknown reasons
<br />

<br />
Court Ranks-&gt; No, no reason for them to be worth more than a badge of honor.
<br />

<br />
Retire Cooldown-&gt; Absolutely not, this is to viable of a strategy amongst both the top and everyone else, it's universal
<br />

<br />
Whatever else you suggested-&gt;I know I hated it when it was suggested!  I just don't remember what it was.
